N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.22 - Subscription defined

State Regulations

An entry of a horse in a sweepstakes is a subscription
to the sweepstakes. An entry or subscription may, before the time of closing, be altered or withdrawn. Notes
